main event: Observers reported seeing 5 unidentified objects with a pattern of yellow lights in San Luis Obispo, California on 2/23/52.
interesting points: The objects were visible for 5 minutes and did not make any noise due to a nearby jet,The lights were similar to those of an airplane but did not blink off and on,Multiple observers had vantage points from both land and sea,There was speculation that the sighting could have been due to one of the numerous aircraft operating in the area,The findings were documented as part of Project Blue Book under possible aircraft.
sighted object: five unidentified objects with yellow lights
witness description: The description includes observations made from a moving vehicle and another person's experience with a similar sighting.
